	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am going to create a human shadowknight. I have already decided this. My question- It is recommended at Everlore, or Castersrealm, I think, to put 5 in str 5 in dex 5 in agi, and 5 in int. What do you all think? <br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
